vn.uiza.libstream.uiza.faucamp.simplertmp.packets

Class VariableBodyRtmpPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • vn.uiza.libstream.uiza.faucamp.simplertmp.packets.RtmpPacket
      • vn.uiza.libstream.uiza.faucamp.simplertmp.packets.VariableBodyRtmpPacket
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Command, Data

    public abstract class VariableBodyRtmpPacket
extends RtmpPacket
    RTMP packet with a "variable" body structure (i.e. the structure of the body depends on some other state/parameter in the packet.

    Examples of this type of packet are Command and Data; this abstract class exists mostly for code re-use.
